        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Civilian Guard A', 3: 'So you\\'re saying the longer that lines run, the worse the odds get... Is surrender truly not an option for us?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 35,
        "ActionId": 35,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Driver', 3: 'What are you saying?!', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 36,
        "ActionId": 36,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Civilian Guard A', 3: 'I\\'m asking if there\\'s a way to keep people alive! Weren\\'t we told that surrender would end the war? That everyone would be safe?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 37,
        "ActionId": 37,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Driver', 3: 'Safe? Remember the Union back then? The Frostheart Emperor doesn\\'t want peace; he wants the world. Surrender, and we\\'ll just become soldiers for his war.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 38,
        "ActionId": 38,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Civilian Guard A', 3: 'He can control the Corrupted! And the Punishing Virus keeps creating abominations. Why aren\\'t we uniting against that instead of fighting each other?!', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 39,
        "ActionId": 39,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Civilian Guard A', 3: 'It\\'s the same with this war. If only there were someone whose call everyone would answer, someone who could rally everyone to help us. Then we wouldn\\'t be sitting here terrified, and our soldiers at the front wouldn\\'t be throwing their lives away!', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
