        "Params": "{1: '1', 3: 'A voice, clear and bright, interrupts the low hum of conversation. Evan stands at the edge of the group, his small hands fisted in the hem of his coat. Though the cold has painted his cheeks a raw red, the look in his eyes is pure, unwavering determination.'}"
    },
