        "Params": "{3: 'Evan opens his mouth, then freezes. He feels like he should have an answer, but the words die on his lips. The truth hits him with sudden clarity: he\\'s only here because everyone he knows is here. His only purpose has been to carry bricks and build walls beside them.'}"
